Provenance
----------

Quoll's live-preview reveal/widget layer (src/webview/cm/decorations/ and the
sibling widget StateFields) is independently implemented. The live-preview
"reveal the Markdown source under the caret" behaviour was informed by prior
CodeMirror-based editors — ixora (Apache-2.0) and the Atomic Editor (MIT) —
but no source from either is vendored or adapted into Quoll; they were
referenced for behaviour only. No notice obligation arises from them.
